donations.donation_comment: My hopes and prayers are with all of you. This has received more attention and accomplished more than any politician. These are the kind of events I would rather fund than 98 per cent of people running for office. Not all but most seem not to have the moral fiber to stand up to party leadership and politics. Thank all the truckers for giving us hope.
Thank you for what you are doing!
Praying for these brave freedom fighters and their families Taking one hour of prayer for all during Eucharistic Adoration today at our Church. Keep up your hope and stay strong!

Thank you guys for what you are doing for all of us !!!
Good luck !!! We will win this !!!
God bless our Truckers and all who are fighting for the cause of individual liberty and freedom, here and in many places around the world.
The truckers and everyone else involved in the convoy: you guys ROCK! Thank you for standing up and making Canadian voices of reason heard.
I pray that all freedom loving people around the world are protected by the full armor of the God. Jesus please protect our children around the world with your light. Amen
